{"tid":1655749,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「孩子」和「崽」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-10-15T08:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T08:19:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c38ed734b7f96284b27885dafbcacbe09a22f56a","tid":1655749,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:19:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191015/20786819/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191015%2F20786819%2F&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9KDV4CCb0oeaEcqd0PTfYOA%3D&h=25dc6f55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191015%2F20786819%2F&h=bf853b7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191015/20786819/</a><br />\n<br />\n「孩子」和「崽」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191015/large/1571036542_4713.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191015%2Flarge%2F1571036542_4713.jpg&h=8bd0124e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周日凌晨3、4點驚雷之後大雨，乍醒關窗──未知遠在獅子山上，正有抗爭者通宵負重齊心合力攻頂，豎立「香港民主女神像」。全部港人是一覺醒來，才見這動人畫面。<br />\n<br />\n過去數月的不幸消息，自殺和被自殺跳樓身亡者，黑衣和全裸的少女浮屍，遭毒毆虐打致殘致死的抗爭者，更恐怖的是可能已有人被無法無天運送大陸懲治&hellip;&hellip;令人髮指，民憤更深反抗更激烈，禁蒙面惡法火上加油。<br />\n<br />\n市民睡不好，情緒低落，有山埃催淚煙後遺症&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n感謝廿多名黑衣抗爭者冒着雷電風雨，由港大校園出發，把已拆件的民女像搬上貨車，摸黑運送上山，裝嵌重組鑽洞固定，終旗幟飄揚屹立在獅子山上。它未必永遠鎮守山頂，但一定永遠鎮守人心。<br />\n<br />\n只有真正愛這土地的香港兒女，才如此堅毅不屈。所有香港孕育栽培默化同心同德同路的人，不論年齡身份貧富智愚，即使靜坐的銀髮族，也是香港的「孩子」，心頭最柔軟的一塊，期盼互相守護。<br />\n<br />\n有「守護孩子」成員在遊行途中擋在黑警前，其中一名便衣躁狂疾呼：「我都係孩子嚟㗎，守護埋我吖嘛！」──哪有資格？黑警只是醜惡政權與陰毒林鄭的「私生物」姑息養奸縱容作惡的「崽」（畜生幼子），要當「孩子」是妄想。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n============================<br />\n<br />\n感謝廿多名黑衣抗爭者冒着雷電風雨，由港大校園出發，把已拆件的民女像搬上貨車，摸黑運送上山，裝嵌重組鑽洞固定，終旗幟飄揚屹立在獅子山上。它未必永遠鎮守山頂，但一定永遠鎮守人心。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}